type: software
title: "rijksmuseum-iconclass-mcp"
abstract: >
  An MCP server for the Iconclass classification system — a universal
  art-subject taxonomy covering 1.3 million notations in 13 languages,
  with full-text and semantic search, hierarchy navigation, and
  collection count overlays.
